==English==
===Noun===
[[Category:English irregular plurals]]
{{en-noun|waterman|watermen}}
#[[Category:Surfing]] A [[man]] skilled in multiple [[acquatic]] disciplines, such as [[surfing]], [[bodysurfing]], undersea [[diving]], [[canoe]] paddling, [[fishing]], etc.
====Usage note====
Describing someone as a ''waterman'' is the highest honour in the surfing community and is reserved to those with long-standing and indisputably significant all-round achievements.
